      <title>Maximum likelihood estimation</title>
      <p>Maximum likelihood estimation is performed using the the log-likelihood function corresponding to Eq. <xref rid="Equ6" ref-type="">4</xref>, namely, 
<disp-formula id="Equ7"><label>5</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M67">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
