    <sec id="Sec7">
      <title>Quantifying changes in homeolog expression bias (<italic>Δ</italic>HEB)</title>
      <p>Let <italic>A</italic> and <italic>B</italic> represent homeologous genes and RNA-seq data is generated under conditions 1 and 2 in <italic>n</italic> biological replicates, leading to mean expression levels <inline-formula id="IEq32"><alternatives><tex-math id="M97">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
